Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个人的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是无法重叠在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这样下去是不行的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷 之后就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙 想要逃掉值日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫逃掉 这本来就不是我们该做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊 别让我们把话挑明了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想把活都推给天枷同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由梦 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏学姐也说过人对待事物经常是三分钟热度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于天枷的事 虽然我也想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们能做的 也只有静观动向而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说不要擅自行动 先静观其变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骚动过一段时间自然消失也不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 之后一段时间内 天枷的事暂时由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟启动了天枷的人是我 我必须承担责任才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我估计会有一段时间不能来参加乐队的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 如果有难处你可一定要跟我们说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想帮天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在就请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢天枷的人 也会敌视她身边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让小恋遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱内 美夏一个人能回家的 别担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我当傻瓜 美夏我可是最尖端科技的结晶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们竟然把我当小孩看待…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在这里在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 义之君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学也在呢 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个提议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提议？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学 这段时间 要不要成为我们家的一员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家的一员？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这件事解决之前 让她一直在我们家住下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟还是小心一点的好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又让你费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是谢谢你的好意 还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 这可是校长命令哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样确实挺好的呢 对吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定？ 就这么决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 小恋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看搞笑Gong Show
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看歌曲Top10
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看搞笑Gong Show
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看歌曲Top10
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看搞笑Gong Show
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看歌曲Top10
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定看这个了吧 樱内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷 你在别人家就不知道客气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你用不着这么说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 美夏可是因为校长一直唠叨个不停才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换言之便是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你就想这么随便地招呼客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说的非常对 那么就请随意看你们喜欢的节目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱内 你挡着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢天枷的人 也会敌视她身边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让小恋遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 便当？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我想让大家一起吃所以做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学喜欢的香蕉三明治也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思呢 让你这么费心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 快来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学又…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 小恋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 没跟你在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛到底在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天没有社团活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}From奈奈佳  知道小恋在哪里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不良少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也确实是想要休息了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有义之君的社团活动 就像是没有草莓的草莓蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}To奈奈佳  就别去打扰她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息的理由也并不是因为这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天没去社团活动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈佳发短信给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 是因为我的原因吧 昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为昨天不在状态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以怕奈奈佳说我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在状态？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 别担心 我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 了解了 要我去跟涉也说一声吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事 我会跟他说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候才能给我个答复
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷美夏那件事 再怎么谨慎认真也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也回应的太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也解决不了问题 我就用我的方式来做出回应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会向PTA和教育委员会提出异议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}PTA：家长教师会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直这么含糊搪塞可不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音姬 你真的不知情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音姬 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由纪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由纪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士最后…了却了自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井同学 因为机器人才让家庭支离破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被夺去了自己的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直是这样认为的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台湾香蕉和厄瓜多尔香蕉 要哪种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱内 随便哪个都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一个香蕉素比较多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然连学生会那边都串通过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 我没有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管樱内你做什么 我都绝对不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人 机器人我绝对不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下 不是你接不接受的问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样 很了解班长的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不全是机器人的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底了解什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人到底能了解什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然之间就失去了父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直伤心 痛苦着 什么办法也想不出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能一直这么哭 你怎能体会我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人把我的一切都夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因为这个 我 我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谢谢你了 勇斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你们是姐姐的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我叫泽井勇斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是懂礼貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们走吧 勇斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是第一次知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长有那么小的一个弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井会生气也是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里还有个这么大的孩子呢 现在被机器人搞得一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气也是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那些事和天枷一点关系都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏至今为止没有相信过任何一个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以说是憎恨人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类只顾自己方便制造出了机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妨碍自己的生活 马上就毫不犹豫地废弃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信人类很险恶 机器人总是扮演着被害者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 我犯了一个非常大的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有因机器人而遭到不幸的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像泽井那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏是机器人 泽井是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但泽井和以前的美夏是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资本主义经济的发展使社会的构成变得更为复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}当经济处于衰退时期 就业者数量下降 收入的减少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}在这不容乐观的形势下 个人收入的变化量也无法与之同步…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷虽然是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 还是得想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}至此 有分析指出这个问题必须由社会与国家相结合来进行解决
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}也就诞生了社会保障问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}日后 社会保障制度…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}From奈奈佳  看外面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是没问题了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃些 多吃些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学的事能平安解决就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋 看你一脸寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得义之做得很对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…那个…寂寞什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是瞒不过奈奈佳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是义之君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去开门哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:20:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈佳 那个 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得义之为了天枷同学这么努力是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真心这么想的 但是 正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望义之为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之为我操心 虽然很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望可以帮义之一把
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和义之一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是恋人 我想两个人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却隐藏着自己真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还撒了「不想让义之为难」 这样的谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直这么压抑着自己 一直挑义之爱听的话说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样根本就不是我 不是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和义之交往以前 还没有这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系本应比青梅竹马更进了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在和义之在一起好痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 我会讨厌自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会开始讨厌义之的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋 很难受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也许已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}嘴里叼着面包说着迟到了迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}在拐角撞到的人是转学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}遇到这种女生的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.72,0:23:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}会说神啊 这种事还真是难碰上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.06,0:23:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}嗯？倒不是说多讨厌…
